32 SUMMARY
3333 This bill amends the laws governing school food service programs to provide free
3344 school lunches to special purpose private schools that receive publicly funded students and
3355 participate in the National School Lunch Program in accordance with 7 Code of Federal
3366 Regulations, Part 210 (2007).
